info.description:
This module contains a collection of YANG definitions
     for AAA operational data.

Cisco IOS-XE operational state data (read-only).
**Category:** Security & AAA
**Paths:** 31

**YANG Model:** [Cisco-IOS-XE-aaa-oper.yang](https://github.com/YangModels/yang/blob/main/vendor/cisco/xe/17181/Cisco-IOS-XE-aaa-oper.yang)
